00:00:52,830 --> 00:00:59,260
♫  Saying too much, there's no "what if"  ♫ 
♫  Might as well go on an adventure  ♫

6
00:00:59,260 --> 00:01:02,780
♫  I stand in the shadows  ♫

7
00:01:02,780 --> 00:01:08,120
♫  Reaching out, waiting for your rescue  ♫

8
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:13,070
♫  Between you and me  ♫ 
♫  Even if the world collapses  ♫

9
00:01:13,070 --> 00:01:17,160
♫  No matter how far the distance  ♫

10
00:01:17,160 --> 00:01:21,620
♫  Nothing can stop our meeting  ♫

11
00:01:21,620 --> 00:01:28,610
♫  Stepping through the long dark night  ♫ 
 ♫  You are standing at the finish line  ♫

12
00:01:28,610 --> 00:01:32,820
♫  Protecting you is my tiny wish  ♫

13
00:01:32,820 --> 00:01:37,170
♫  Goodbye to the shy me of the past  ♫

14
00:01:37,170 --> 00:01:42,820
♫  Because of you, I have become a little braver  ♫

15
00:01:42,820 --> 00:01:46,250
   

16
00:01:46,250 --> 00:01:49,940
   
   

17
00:01:49,940 --> 00:01:51,870
Qi Qi.

18
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:53,680
Qi Qi.

19
00:01:57,550 --> 00:01:59,790
This is for you.

20
00:01:59,790 --> 00:02:01,510
Surprised?

21
00:02:01,510 --> 00:02:04,400
This is a gift from the three of us.

22
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:10,620
Qi Qi, we hope you can freely pursue what you love.

23
00:02:16,580 --> 00:02:19,390
The video was your idea, right?

24
00:02:19,390 --> 00:02:22,230
That wasn't me. That was Jing Xi Chi.

25
00:02:22,230 --> 00:02:24,640
He did all the editing and video work.

26
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:25,900
Didn't I tell you not to say that?

27
00:02:25,900 --> 00:02:28,140
Don't be so modest.

28
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:32,540
The bakery said they couldn't make a big cake in time.

29
00:02:32,540 --> 00:02:35,300
This one is small, but it's really delicious.

30
00:02:36,270 --> 00:02:38,020
Thank you.

31
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:41,340
Editing the video must've been tough.

32
00:02:41,340 --> 00:02:43,950
Also...

33
00:02:43,950 --> 00:02:45,550
I didn't understand before.

34
00:02:45,550 --> 00:02:47,550
I shouldn't have said those things.

35
00:02:47,550 --> 00:02:51,430
You'll definitely keep getting better at soccer

36
00:02:51,430 --> 00:02:53,460
and achieve your dream.

37
00:02:54,620 --> 00:02:56,900
I've already forgotten about it.

38
00:03:02,950 --> 00:03:06,340
Thank you all so much.

39
00:03:06,340 --> 00:03:08,110
Don't mention it.

40
00:03:10,500 --> 00:03:14,300
Qi Qi, how about a hug?

41
00:03:15,740 --> 00:03:19,470
Let me hold that for you. You two, hug.

42
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:24,180
Qi Qi, don't forget me after you transfer classes.

43
00:03:24,180 --> 00:03:28,580
I won't. I'll never forget you.

44
00:03:28,580 --> 00:03:31,300
You mustn't forget me.

45
00:03:31,300 --> 00:03:34,120
I'll never forget you.

46
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,911
No crying.

47
00:03:35,911 --> 00:03:38,521
All right, all right.

48
00:03:40,380 --> 00:03:43,340
I won't forget you guys either.

49
00:03:45,230 --> 00:03:47,670
Let's have a hug too.

50
00:03:48,740 --> 00:03:51,270
After all, we're parting ways.

51
00:04:11,780 --> 00:04:13,550
Thank you.

52
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:16,620
It's nothing.

53
00:04:16,620 --> 00:04:18,790
- It's no big deal. 
 - I'll get going now.

54
00:04:18,790 --> 00:04:22,140
- All right, text me when you get home. 
 - Don't mention it.

55
00:04:22,140 --> 00:04:23,180
- Bye-bye. 
 - I'll get going.

56
00:04:23,180 --> 00:04:25,260
- Bye-bye. 
 - Bye-bye.

57
00:04:25,260 --> 00:04:27,790
Be careful on your way home.

58
00:04:55,640 --> 00:04:57,600
 You're pretty good with computers. 

59
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,380
I never thought about it before.

60
00:04:59,380 --> 00:05:04,430
I always thought that you couldn't do anything else besides playing soccer.

61
00:05:04,430 --> 00:05:06,740
Well, it depends on whether I actually want to do it.

62
00:05:06,740 --> 00:05:10,990
If I don't do something well, it's simply because I'm not interested.

63
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:23,230
You don't want Qi Qi to transfer, do you?

64
00:05:24,810 --> 00:05:27,160
Why are you suddenly asking this?

65
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:32,640
Nothing, I just feel like you treat Qi Qi differently.

66
00:05:36,450 --> 00:05:41,380
Once Qi Qi transfers to art class, stop deliberately doing poorly on exams.

67
00:06:10,740 --> 00:06:11,740
Hello, Huan Er?

68
00:06:11,740 --> 00:06:15,690
Qi Qi, did you see the field trip info I sent you?

69
00:06:15,690 --> 00:06:17,300
 Yeah, I saw it. 

70
00:06:17,300 --> 00:06:20,080
 I really want to go, but my mom definitely won't let me. 

71
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:23,670
She just told me I have a bunch of tutoring classes in the summer.

72
00:06:24,300 --> 00:06:27,790
 But it's school break. Why won't she let you go? 

73
00:06:27,790 --> 00:06:30,180
It's not just a trip. It's an educational trip.

74
00:06:30,180 --> 00:06:33,110
We'll visit museums to learn.

75
00:06:33,110 --> 00:06:34,300
Besides, everyone's going.

76
00:06:34,300 --> 00:06:38,430
Me, Jing Xi Chi, Xin Yan, Song Cong... everyone.

77
00:06:38,430 --> 00:06:39,590
 Are you coming? 

78
00:06:39,590 --> 00:06:41,350
Liao Xin Yan is going too?

79
00:06:41,350 --> 00:06:43,010
 Yeah. 

80
00:06:43,010 --> 00:06:45,040
Are you coming?

81
00:06:47,820 --> 00:06:50,790
I probably won't be able to go.

82
00:06:53,470 --> 00:06:54,640
All right then.

83
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:56,460
Bye-bye.

84
00:07:06,450 --> 00:07:07,490
How much?

85
00:07:07,490 --> 00:07:08,820
Ten yuan.

86
00:07:08,820 --> 00:07:10,380
Here.

87
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:24,620
Hey, you two didn't wait for me.

88
00:07:24,620 --> 00:07:27,210
- Huan Er. 
 - Xin Yan!

89
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:32,440
I didn't see you the entire break. I kept asking you out. Where were you?

90
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:34,680
I went back to my hometown for a few days.

91
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,820
I talked to the group leader earlier.

92
00:07:38,820 --> 00:07:41,940
We're sharing a room. We can have a nice chat tonight.

93
00:07:41,940 --> 00:07:44,260
This is really good.

94
00:07:44,260 --> 00:07:45,860
Huan Er.

95
00:07:46,740 --> 00:07:48,300
Qi Qi?

96
00:07:48,300 --> 00:07:49,910
You signed up?

97
00:07:49,910 --> 00:07:51,590
I thought you weren't coming.

98
00:07:51,590 --> 00:07:54,080
Yeah, I signed up. I signed up the day after you told me about it.

99
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:56,500
I was worried I might not make it, so I didn't tell you.

100
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:59,550
That's amazing. How did you convince your mom?

101
00:07:59,550 --> 00:08:02,740
I have my ways.

102
00:08:02,740 --> 00:08:05,430
- This is great. 
 - Looks like everyone is here now.

103
00:08:05,430 --> 00:08:07,260
Driver, let's go.

104
00:08:07,260 --> 00:08:09,600
- The bus is leaving, sit down. 
 - Xin Yan, I wanted to...

105
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,740
Sit down...

106
00:08:10,740 --> 00:08:11,870
We'll talk later.

107
00:08:11,870 --> 00:08:14,590
- Okay. Sit down. 
 - Okay.

108
00:08:17,030 --> 00:08:19,880
Jing Xi Chi, you should be the class president for this trip.

109
00:08:19,880 --> 00:08:21,300
You're really good at organizing.

110
00:08:21,300 --> 00:08:24,360
No way. Let Song Cong do it.

111
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:46,100
All right, students, get off the bus. Grab your luggage.

112
00:08:46,740 --> 00:08:49,870
You still haven't told me how you convinced your mom.

113
00:08:49,870 --> 00:08:54,380
Me? I told my mom I'm going on an educational tour with my classmates.

114
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:56,740
It's for learning, not for fun.

115
00:08:56,740 --> 00:08:59,350
Huan Er, can I borrow some of the mosquito repellent you were using?

116
00:08:59,350 --> 00:09:01,140
That's Qi Qi's.

117
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:04,900
Qi Qi, can you share your mosquito repellent with Xin Yan?

118
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:12,020
Thanks.

119
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:16,900
Xin Yan, spray some on me, too.

120
00:09:16,900 --> 00:09:19,970
- Sure. 
 - Here, look.

121
00:09:19,970 --> 00:09:21,900
That's enough.

122
00:09:21,900 --> 00:09:23,100
Song Cong, do you want some?

123
00:09:23,100 --> 00:09:25,004
- I'll do it myself. 
 - All right.

124
00:09:25,004 --> 00:09:26,070
Thanks.

125
00:09:26,070 --> 00:09:27,990
All right, students, your room keys are ready.

126
00:09:27,990 --> 00:09:29,350
Let me do a roll call.

127
00:09:29,350 --> 00:09:31,310
- Chen Huan Er. 
 - Here.

128
00:09:31,310 --> 00:09:32,660
Liao Xin Yan.

129
00:09:32,660 --> 00:09:34,050
Okay, you two are sharing a room.

130
00:09:34,050 --> 00:09:36,470
There was one more person who came later. Qi Qi.

131
00:09:36,470 --> 00:09:38,600
You'll have a room to yourself.

132
00:09:40,380 --> 00:09:41,740
Sir, what about us?

133
00:09:41,740 --> 00:09:42,830
Come with me for a moment.

134
00:09:42,830 --> 00:09:47,500
Qi Qi, if you don't mind, you can share a bed with me.

135
00:09:47,500 --> 00:09:49,470
It's fine; let's just go with the arrangement.

136
00:09:49,470 --> 00:09:50,880
Don't be like that.

137
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:54,080
I really didn't know you were coming. How about this:

138
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:56,260
you take the bed, and I'll sleep on the floor.

139
00:09:56,260 --> 00:09:58,560
No need, I can stay alone.

140
00:09:58,560 --> 00:09:59,900
- Come on, let's share a room. 
 - Qi Qi!

141
00:09:59,900 --> 00:10:03,620
Don't be shy. Actually, you two can take the bed, and I'll take the floor.

142
00:10:03,620 --> 00:10:06,210
I roll onto the floor in my sleep anyway.

143
00:10:07,190 --> 00:10:11,230
Let's stay together, please...

144
00:10:11,230 --> 00:10:12,780
All right then.

145
00:10:12,780 --> 00:10:15,740
Okay. Song Cong, the mosquito repellent.

146
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:18,220
- I'll put it here. 
 - Thanks.

147
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:20,900
Looks like everyone else is heading that way.

148
00:10:20,900 --> 00:10:22,110
- Let's go. 
 - Yeah, let's go.

149
00:10:22,110 --> 00:10:24,000
- Thanks, sir. 
 - You're welcome.

150
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,800
We're sharing a room.

151
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,660
What are you looking at?

152
00:10:33,660 --> 00:10:38,070
I feel like there's some tension between them.

153
00:10:38,070 --> 00:10:39,860
Tension?

154
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:42,540
Stop making things up.

155
00:10:42,540 --> 00:10:47,260
You don't understand. Girls do everything holding hands.

156
00:10:47,260 --> 00:10:49,510
What? Are you jealous?

157
00:11:03,830 --> 00:11:05,600
Finally, we're at the park.

158
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,740
What is this, a study trip?

159
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:08,380
We've been learning all day.

160
00:11:08,380 --> 00:11:11,500
Honestly, this isn't much different from regular school.

161
00:11:13,950 --> 00:11:15,590
Hey, there are boats.

162
00:11:15,590 --> 00:11:17,990
Wouldn't it be fun to go boating?

163
00:11:17,990 --> 00:11:19,740
Let's pair up and race.

164
00:11:19,740 --> 00:11:21,070
That'll be even better.

165
00:11:21,070 --> 00:11:22,830
I'm not feeling well today.

166
00:11:22,830 --> 00:11:24,990
I'll team up with Huan Er.

167
00:11:24,990 --> 00:11:26,540
Huan Er...

168
00:11:30,590 --> 00:11:32,620
How about mixed-gender teams?

169
00:11:32,620 --> 00:11:34,070
That way, it'll be safer.

170
00:11:34,070 --> 00:11:36,640
Sounds good.

171
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:40,084
Xin Yan, since you're not feeling well, you team up with Jing Xi Chi.

172
00:11:40,084 --> 00:11:42,230
He's a sportsman.

173
00:11:42,230 --> 00:11:45,190
Qi Qi, you team up with Song Cong.

174
00:11:45,190 --> 00:11:46,710
Is that okay?

175
00:11:47,730 --> 00:11:49,020
What about you?

176
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:50,590
Me?

177
00:11:50,590 --> 00:11:51,830
I'll be a one-person team.

178
00:11:51,830 --> 00:11:54,190
I can take you all on by myself.

179
00:11:54,190 --> 00:11:55,380
Let's go.

180
00:11:55,380 --> 00:11:57,420
Chen Huan Er, you think you're so tough?

181
00:11:57,420 --> 00:11:59,600
- I'm going to crush you. 
 - Hurry up!

182
00:12:08,110 --> 00:12:11,760
Jing Xi Chi, what do you like to do in your free time?

183
00:12:11,760 --> 00:12:13,070
Winning, of course.

184
00:12:13,070 --> 00:12:15,860
Pedal harder. Come on, catch up to her.

185
00:12:17,830 --> 00:12:19,620
I'm coming for you, Chen Huan Er.

186
00:12:19,620 --> 00:12:22,710
Let's just go at a steady pace.

187
00:12:22,710 --> 00:12:25,770
Safety first. No need to compete with them.

188
00:12:34,470 --> 00:12:35,740
Chen Huan Er.

189
00:12:35,740 --> 00:12:37,260
I'm coming for you!

190
00:12:37,260 --> 00:12:38,950
Don't run!

191
00:12:38,950 --> 00:12:41,230
Come at me.

192
00:12:41,230 --> 00:12:42,590
Come on, pedal harder.

193
00:12:42,590 --> 00:12:44,910
We're catching up...

194
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:49,000
No!

195
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,110
Chen Huan Er!

196
00:12:50,110 --> 00:12:51,660
Huan Er!

197
00:12:53,660 --> 00:12:54,950
Huan Er!

198
00:12:54,950 --> 00:12:56,740
- Huan Er! 
 - Huan Er!

199
00:12:56,740 --> 00:12:58,670
Climb on board.

200
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:03,190
Are you okay?

201
00:13:03,190 --> 00:13:04,470
Huan Er, how are you?

202
00:13:04,470 --> 00:13:06,170
Are you all right?

203
00:13:10,140 --> 00:13:12,350
I swallowed too much water.

204
00:13:18,500 --> 00:13:20,070
Are you okay?

205
00:13:20,070 --> 00:13:22,740
- How are you? 
 - I'm fine.

206
00:13:22,740 --> 00:13:24,590
You should take Huan Er back to her room.

207
00:13:24,590 --> 00:13:26,230
She's definitely caught a cold.

208
00:13:26,230 --> 00:13:28,830
I'll go buy her some medicine.

209
00:13:28,830 --> 00:13:30,540
Thanks, Qi Qi.

210
00:13:30,540 --> 00:13:32,740
You're welcome. Go on.

211
00:13:35,830 --> 00:13:38,420
Qi Qi, where are you going?

212
00:13:38,420 --> 00:13:41,020
I'm going to buy medicine for Huan Er.

213
00:13:41,020 --> 00:13:42,230
I'll go with you.

214
00:13:42,230 --> 00:13:45,470
No thanks. I can go by myself.

215
00:13:45,470 --> 00:13:48,590
Jing Xi Chi, you were too competitive earlier.

216
00:13:48,590 --> 00:13:50,900
Good thing Huan Er knows how to swim.

217
00:13:52,350 --> 00:13:55,590
I didn't mean for that to happen.

218
00:13:55,590 --> 00:13:58,710
How about I go apologize to her?

219
00:13:58,710 --> 00:14:00,470
Then hurry up.

220
00:14:00,470 --> 00:14:02,310
All right, I'll go.

221
00:14:06,740 --> 00:14:08,780
Song Cong.

222
00:14:08,780 --> 00:14:11,080
Do you know where the pharmacy is?

223
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:13,140
There's a pretty busy street near the hotel.

224
00:14:13,140 --> 00:14:15,310
There should be one there.

225
00:14:15,310 --> 00:14:16,990
Can you take me there?

226
00:14:16,990 --> 00:14:18,900
I don't know the way.

227
00:14:18,900 --> 00:14:21,950
Well... why don't you ask the front desk?

228
00:14:21,950 --> 00:14:23,710
I've got something to do.

229
00:14:23,710 --> 00:14:25,270
Okay.

230
00:14:56,990 --> 00:15:00,260
 Song Cong, have one too. 

231
00:15:00,260 --> 00:15:02,230
 I've had them before. 

232
00:15:07,950 --> 00:15:10,470
 Let's have a hug too. 

233
00:15:30,540 --> 00:15:31,830
What are you doing?

234
00:15:31,830 --> 00:15:32,960
Why are you out here?

235
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:35,080
You might catch a cold.

236
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,990
I just took a hot shower.

237
00:15:37,990 --> 00:15:39,880
I'm feeling warm.

238
00:15:40,420 --> 00:15:41,780
Where's Xin Yan?

239
00:15:41,780 --> 00:15:44,900
She just had dinner with me.

240
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:47,380
But she got caught up chatting with her clubmates

241
00:15:47,380 --> 00:15:51,070
and I didn't have much to say, so I left.

242
00:15:55,870 --> 00:15:58,660
Here, I bought these for you.

243
00:15:58,660 --> 00:16:00,990
Why did you buy oranges?

244
00:16:00,990 --> 00:16:02,990
I wanted to apologize to you.

245
00:16:04,540 --> 00:16:11,500
You see, when we were boating earlier, I went overboard.

246
00:16:11,500 --> 00:16:13,190
I'm sorry.

247
00:16:16,770 --> 00:16:18,620
It's okay.

248
00:16:20,710 --> 00:16:26,090
If anyone should apologize, it should be me.

249
00:16:28,070 --> 00:16:31,470
I wasn't thinking clearly back at the park earlier.

250
00:16:31,470 --> 00:16:34,110
I ended up splitting you and Qi Qi up.

251
00:16:34,950 --> 00:16:37,020
Big Brother, I'm sorry.

252
00:16:37,020 --> 00:16:39,070
I'm really sorry.

253
00:16:39,070 --> 00:16:41,710
What are you saying? Just eat your orange.

254
00:16:41,710 --> 00:16:44,990
I'm telling you, these oranges are amazing!

255
00:16:44,990 --> 00:16:46,500
You haven't even tried them yet.

256
00:16:46,500 --> 00:16:49,380
They're full of vitamin C and they help prevent colds.

257
00:16:49,380 --> 00:16:50,470
You mustn't get sick now.

258
00:16:50,470 --> 00:16:51,830
I'm perfectly healthy.

259
00:16:51,830 --> 00:16:55,260
I run every day, and my dad teaches me martial arts.

260
00:16:55,260 --> 00:16:57,327
Here it goes. I wonder if it's sweet.

261
00:16:57,327 --> 00:16:58,417
You go first.

262
00:16:58,417 --> 00:17:01,447
- Eat mine. 
 - It's too big.

263
00:17:01,447 --> 00:17:03,177
Try it.

