556
00:33:45,857 --> 00:33:48,617
Why isn't Chen Huan Er here yet?

557
00:33:48,617 --> 00:33:52,087
She said she made plans to eat with Qi Qi.

558
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:55,097
Maybe they have something to talk about.

559
00:33:55,097 --> 00:33:57,427
