562
00:34:06,857 --> 00:34:08,697
Her phone's off.

563
00:34:08,697 --> 00:34:11,127
Her phone's off?

564
00:34:11,127 --> 00:34:13,017
Call Qi Qi.

565
00:34:17,647 --> 00:34:20,567
 Sorry, the number you dialed is powered off. 

566
00:34:20,567 --> 00:34:23,167
- Hers is off too. 
  - Please try again later. 

567
00:34:23,167 --> 00:34:28,047
A few days ago, my mom warned me that the area near our school has been a bit unsafe lately.

568
00:34:28,047 --> 00:34:30,417
Could something have happened to them?

569
00:34:48,087 --> 00:34:49,857
Chen Huan Er!

570
00:34:57,760 --> 00:34:59,737
- What are you two doing here? 
 - What do you mean?

571
00:34:59,737 --> 00:35:01,558
