572
00:35:01,558 --> 00:35:03,692
You didn't answer our calls. What were you doing with your phone?

573
00:35:03,692 --> 00:35:07,007
- My battery died. 
 - Then what are you doing here?

574
00:35:07,007 --> 00:35:09,007
I was waiting for Qi Qi, but she never showed up.

575
00:35:09,007 --> 00:35:11,967
So I wandered around, and ended up here.

576
00:35:11,967 --> 00:35:13,857
All right, enough talking. Let's go home first.

577
00:35:13,857 --> 00:35:15,417
