580
00:35:18,697 --> 00:35:20,440
- Don't you dare! Don't tell her. 
 - I'll tell her.

581
00:35:20,440 --> 00:35:22,672
- Please, I'm begging you. 
 - I'm telling her.

582
00:35:22,672 --> 00:35:25,497
