586
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:43,137
Here, Song Cong, pass the ball.

587
00:35:43,137 --> 00:35:44,777
I want to try the "Hand of God."

588
00:35:44,777 --> 00:35:47,447
What's the "Hand of God"?

589
00:35:47,447 --> 00:35:49,337
You don't know?

590
00:35:49,967 --> 00:35:52,967
In the 1986 Mexico World Cup quarterfinals,

591
00:35:52,967 --> 00:35:57,607
