611
00:37:53,600 --> 00:37:55,090
Should we call the police?

612
00:37:55,090 --> 00:37:57,360
They know we're from Tianhe No. 1. Will they come after us?

613
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:58,937
No, they won't.

614
00:37:58,937 --> 00:38:01,167
We should just go home and tell our parents.

615
00:38:01,167 --> 00:38:03,497
We can't tell my mom.

616
00:38:04,897 --> 00:38:06,777
How about this?

617
00:38:06,777 --> 00:38:10,377
Tomorrow, I'll talk to the teacher.

618
00:38:10,377 --> 00:38:13,447
You two wait here. I'll go buy some medicine for Huan Er.

619
00:38:13,447 --> 00:38:14,737
It's okay, Song Cong.

620
00:38:14,737 --> 00:38:17,247
I'll be fine by tomorrow.

621
00:38:23,400 --> 00:38:26,909
Chen Huan Er, did you have to grab me so tightly?

622
00:38:26,909 --> 00:38:28,007
Look at this mark.

623
00:38:28,007 --> 00:38:30,937
