624
00:38:35,257 --> 00:38:37,967
I mean, what if you ran back to fight them?

625
00:38:37,967 --> 00:38:40,360
I wouldn't be able to save you.

626
00:38:40,360 --> 00:38:42,040
Come on!

627
00:38:42,040 --> 00:38:44,646
Honestly, I might have been able to take on those three.

628
00:38:44,646 --> 00:38:47,217
I was just about to strike back.

