00:38:47,217 --> 00:38:48,337
Yeah, right.

630
00:38:48,337 --> 00:38:50,857
You were almost put in a choke hold.

631
00:38:50,857 --> 00:38:52,167
I'm a sportsman, you know.

632
00:38:52,167 --> 00:38:54,857
My dad is a martial arts coach.

633
00:38:54,857 --> 00:38:57,400
Anyway, next time there's trouble, save Song Cong first.

634
00:38:57,400 --> 00:38:59,180
I don't need your help.

